In charge of overall marketing initiatives at Avetics. The role involves the use and creation of digital and social marketing campaigns to reach out to the target audience.

1) Utilise digital and social media marketing to deliver content to target audiences
2) In-charge of social media accounts and campaigns
2) In-charge of Search Engine Marketing
3) Updating of website
4) Develop creative marketing plan for new drone product/services

Technical Skills and Competencies Trainee will learn during SGUnited Traineeship Programme:

1. Usage of Adwords and google analytics
2. Usage of Linkedin ads
3. Usage of Squarespace CMS
4. Preparing marketing campaign materials
5. Design skills using Adobe Illustrator

Highest Qualification: Polytechnic Diploma

Eligibility Criteria for SGUnitedTraineeships:•Singapore Citizen or Permanent Resident; anda.Graduated or graduating in calendar year 2019 or 2020 from ITEs, polytechnics, universities, or other educational institutions (e.g. private universities and overseas institutions); orb.Graduated earlier from above institutions and completed National Service in 2019 or 2020

